data.title: 1936) – Find a Grave Gedenkstätte
data.meta_description: Bob Lee was brought to Dunlap for burial Saturday. He had passed away in Council Bluffs on Thursday. Robert Nathan Lee was born June 30, 1878 at Souneman, Illinois, and passed away April 2, 1936 at the age of 57 years, at his home in Council Bluffs. When a small boy he moved with his parents to Dunlap where he lived...
